{"tid":219423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個成日捐錢比孤兒院同做義工","createTime":"2017-04-27T08:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T11:47:56.000Z","uid":36770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e05bab76c97c5c217a023974b1c8965c70531677","tid":219423,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"我為我自己做這些事而感到驕傲😊<br />\n我非常喜歡做這些事，我渴望天天也可以做這些事👍😁<br />\n幫助別人令我感到興奮😄"},{"pid":"20d39b94abed3676225fa44dcf11f08724809a50","tid":219423,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"此post已完"},{"pid":"eae7a8e1ea8ba56ab3a3714fc8ddedbb750e6c3b","tid":219423,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此post已完</blockquote><br />\n你有事情需要我幫助嗎？😄<br />\n幫助別人是我的樂趣，我很樂意為你服務"},{"pid":"0b4d321ab657a6a189ed07c24672de7c0d7d68f4","tid":219423,"uid":22564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"唔怕老實講我真係好需要人捐錢比我"},{"pid":"c43ccb222517835cf45239339937f248b4728b21","tid":219423,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怕老實講我真係好需要人捐錢比我</blockquote><br />\n你去吃屎吧你😊"},{"pid":"a9bf452113d2f6f6b93c57ed2343836e35c8ba29","tid":219423,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"422832211dcc8083f8650a9b10119a9904539035","tid":219423,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地，有錢佬永遠唔會做義工</blockquote><br />\n我就是成功的例子😄"},{"pid":"701b5d39573a1817b4f8bba5ee5f0413757a8386","tid":219423,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港地，有錢佬永遠唔會做義工</blockquote><br />\n我就是成功的例子😄</blockquote><br />\n我不算是有錢人，我每次捐錢都是捐1元過去"},{"pid":"946ae436353534658f4e57857eabbfc0cc63fa62","tid":219423,"uid":17189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">樓主係大陸狗黎(已自認)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F161112_2d962b7cb80e281c2fa2573829c89a1e.jpg&h=4ed886d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係樓主之前個名-連尼住(大佬)</span></strong></span><br />\n讀垃圾OU HD，打字用拼音。<br />\n之後俾巴打圍屌，死不悔改之餘，<br />\n仲笑鳩人讀書少，唔抵得人識打拼音！<br />\n堅稱自己係土生土長嘅香港人喎~~<br />\n<br />\n就算識打字嗰陣都要轉channel去諗嗰個字嘅蝗語點讀，再打出嚟。<br />\n點都慢過用倉頡速成就咁諗點打好撚多<br />\n除非佢本身就係蝗語channel，又或者講慣蝗語<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}